com.robopupu.api.graph

Class Graph<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.graph.Graph<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The parametrized output type of the Graph.

    public class Graph<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Graph is a builder utility for constructing graphs consisting of Nodes.
